<typeStatus box="[934,982,693,717]" pageId="10" pageNumber="361">type</typeStatus>
locality name (Samarkand, a city in 
<collectingCountry box="[151,283,727,752]" name="Uzbekistan" pageId="10" pageNumber="361">Uzbekistan</collectingCountry>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
